{
  "text": "For further analysis of the spike response of each DIN, membrane potential traces were resampled at 5000 Hz and imported to Matlab (Version 7.9, Mathworks, Natick, USA). All data analysis and modelling was done in Matlab, using custom-written scripts. For a detailed description of the electrophysiological methods, see [CITATION_1] .",
